# The bpmn-design skill sources are vendored into
# src/processDocs/bpmnDesignSkill.generated.ts with LF line endings and a content
# hash (BPMN_DESIGN_VERSION). The byte-for-byte pack test compares the on-disk
# bytes against that embedded copy, and the hash is shipped into user folders for
# staleness detection — so the sources must stay LF on every checkout. Without
# this, core.autocrlf=true (Windows) rewrites them to CRLF: the pack test fails and
# a re-pack would flip the hash. eol=lf overrides autocrlf for these paths.
bpmn-design/** text eol=lf
bpmn-design-app/** text eol=lf
src/processDocs/bpmnDesignSkill.generated.ts text eol=lf
